title: Microsoft Azure Firewall: Health
agents: azure_v2
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the health status of Microsoft Azure Firewalls.
 The health metric represents the overall health state of the firewall
 as a percentage.

 You can configure the warning and critical levels using the rule
 "Azure Firewall Health".

 In order to use this check, you need to configure the Azure special agent.

discovery:
 One service is created for each Azure Firewall.
